irst Luxury Hotel, Where Mohammad Ali Jinnah Played Pool &amp; India’s First Film Screening Was Hosted" title="From a unifying symbol, Vande Mataram was recast by Jinnah as a sectarian test of loyalty, used to question Muslim commitment to the idea of Pakistan. (Image: X)" data-src="https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Untitled-design-2026-02-05T143548.817-2026-02-c0de428e014ee6f0dc8051481e0b6e9d-16x9.jpg?impolicy=website&amp;width=540&amp;height=406" class="jsx-2266615697 lazyload"/></figure></a><div class="jsx-943af71aa0bf0d53 twrtcol"><div class="jsx-943af71aa0bf0d53 rowrp"><ul class="jsx-943af71aa0bf0d53 comporow listingUl"><li class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f dflxcl"><div class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f left"><h3 class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f"><a href="/opinion/opinion-india-watches-as-a-rising-reconciliatory-jamaat-takes-on-bnp-in-bangladesh-elections-ws-bl-9896213.html" class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f comporowttl clsinln">India Watches As A Rising, Reconciliatory Jamaat Takes On BNP In Bangladesh Elections</a></h3></div><a href="/opinion/opinion-india-watches-as-a-rising-reconciliatory-jamaat-takes-on-bnp-in-bangladesh-elections-ws-bl-9896213.html" class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f"><figure class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Ameer of Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami, Dr Shafiqur Rahman, with retired senior military officers" title="Ameer of Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami, Dr Shafiqur Rahman, with retired senior military officers. Image/News18" data-src="https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/01/Ameer-of-Bangladesh-Jamaat-e-Islami-Dr-Shafiqur-Rahman-with-retired-senior-military-officers-2026-01-5f288956c94a5bcbd4e11278c16d5db7-16x9.jpg?impolicy=website&amp;width=160&amp;height=120" class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f lazyload"/><div class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f compthreicon "></div></figure></a><div class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f strycomment"></div></li><li class="jsx-8b683815b1c7e8f dflxcl"><div class="jsx