ugh Rahul Bhat’s chilling performance, crafting a thriller that unsettles long after it ends.","post_type":"text","story_id":9917265,"updated_at":"2026-02-20 13:03:51","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/movies/reviews/kennedy-review-rahul-bhat-delivers-career-best-performance-in-anurag-kashyaps-darkest-film-yet-9917265.html","weburl_r":"/movies/reviews/kennedy-review-rahul-bhat-delivers-career-best-performance-in-anurag-kashyaps-darkest-film-yet-9917265.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Bollywood","Movies"],"categories":[{"id":1769017,"name":"Bollywood","slug":"bollywood","parent":15,"permalink":1},{"id":15,"name":"Movies","slug":"movies","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-02-14 17:03:34","display_headline":"Assi Review: Taapsee Pannu, Kani Kusruti Power Anubhav Sinha’s Gut-Wrenching Film With Fierce Conviction","headline":"Assi Review: Taapsee Pannu, Kani Kusruti Power Anubhav Sinha’s Gut-Wrenching Film With Fierce Conviction","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/FotoJet-2026-02-14T162009.834-2026-02-f5e88f6b91ee45cbd3f14727f6e6f10e-3x2.jpg","caption":"Assi is all set to hit theatres on February 20. ","alt":"Assi Review, Assi Movie Review, Assi, Anubhav Sinha, Taapsee Pannu, Kani Kusruti"},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/jpeg","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/FotoJet-2026-02-14T162009.834-2026-02-f5e88f6b91ee45cbd3f14727f6e6f10e.jpg","caption":"Assi is all set to hit theatres on February 20. ","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/FotoJet-2026-02-14T162009.834-2026-02-f5e88f6b91ee45cbd3f14727f6e6f10e-16x9.jpg"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/FotoJet-2026-02-14T162009.834-2026-02-f5e88f6b91ee45cbd3f14727f6e6f10e-4x3.jpg"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/FotoJet-2026-02-14T162009.834-2026-02-f5e88f6b91ee45cbd3f14727f6e6f10e-3x2.jpg"}}},"intro":"After Mulk, Taapsee Pannu dons the lawyer's robe once a