fence, and social issues in these regions. Her work includes in-depth reporting on the conflict in Manipur, and she also closely tracks developments in Bangladesh.\r\nShe has been awarded the UN–Laadli Award for gender-sensitive human-interest reporting and is a notable alumna of the International Visitor Leadership Program (IVLP).She has also been honoured with State Shishusree Award and has got 2025 MASA Women Achiever's Award . She tweets at @KamalikaSengupt","avtar":"assets/images/IMG_6383-2025-07-288b330729cd36987232498c618dd064-scaled.jpeg","website":"","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KamalikaSengupt?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor","facebook":"","instagram":"","fullbio":"","author_type":"digital","author_location":"","author_blogname":"","company":"","youtube":"","linkedin":"","status":"1"}],"categories":[{"id":1744147,"name":"Elections","slug":"elections","parent":0,"permalink":1},{"id":14,"name":"Politics","slug":"politics","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-03-04 10:24:08","display_headline":"TMC Finalises Bengal Polls Candidate List; Age, Performance Review \u0026 Youth Push To Shape Strategy","headline":"TMC Finalises Bengal Polls Candidate List; Age, Performance Review \u0026 Youth Push To Shape Strategy","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Bengal-2026-02-4c7d9f88900776db211a1cb1b61dfa11-3x2.jpg","caption":"While speculation continues to mount, the final list will be cleared by chief minister Mamata Banerjee after discussions with Abhishek Banerjee. (PTI)","alt":"While speculation continues to mount, the final list will be cleared by chief minister Mamata Banerjee after discussions with Abhishek Banerjee. (PTI)"},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/jpeg","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Bengal-2026-02-4c7d9f88900776db211a1cb1b61dfa11.jpg","caption":"While speculation continues to mount, the final list will be cleared by chief minister Mamata Banerjee after discussions with Abhishek Banerjee. (PTI)","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Bengal-2026-02-4c7d9f88900776db211a1cb1b61dfa11-16x9.jpg"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Bengal-2026-02-4c7d9f88900776db211a1cb1b61dfa11-4x3.jpg"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/02/Bengal-2026-02-4c7d9f88900776db211a1cb1b61dfa11-3x2.jpg"}}},"intro":"With nearly 15 years of anti-incumbency working against the party, the leadership is believed to be keen on introducing fresh faces and giving prominence to younger candidates","liveblog_api_url":{"status":0,"title":"","blog_url":""},"has_video":false,"meta_description":"With nearly 15 years of anti-incumbency working against the party, the leadership is believed to be keen on introducing fresh faces and giving prominence to younger candidates","post_type":"text","gif_n18_images":{"url":null,"alt":null},"story_id":9941637,"updated_at":"2026-03-04 10:24:08","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/elections/tmc-finalises-bengal-polls-candidate-list-age-performance-review-youth-push-to-shape-strategy-ws-l-9941637.html","weburl_r":"/elections/tmc-finalises-bengal-polls-candidate-list-age-performance-review-youth-push-to-shape-strategy-ws-l-9941637.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Elections","Politics"],"author_byline":[{"id":"22693","english_name":"Saurabh Verma","slug":"saurabh_verma","nicename":"","blog_title":"","author_email":"Saurabh.Verma@nw18.com","designation":"Senior Sub-editor","author_bio":"Saurabh Verma covers general, national and international day-to-day news for News18.com as a Chief Sub-editor. He keenly observes politics. You can follow him on Twitter --twitter.com/saurabhkverma19","avtar":"","website":"","twitter":"https://twitter.com/saurabhkverma19","facebook":"","instagram":"","fullbio":"","author_type":"digital","author_location":"","author_blogname":"","company":"","youtube":"","linkedin":"","status":"1"}],"categories":[{"id":1744147,"na