tps://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772625292_RJTePVeL9q-SHOWSHA-VAL-5jpg-rwGT5cnFc3-1200x720.jpg","caption":"","alt":""},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/jpeg","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772625292_RJTePVeL9q-SHOWSHA-VAL-5jpg-rwGT5cnFc3.jpg","caption":"News18","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772625292_RJTePVeL9q-SHOWSHA-VAL-5jpg-rwGT5cnFc3-1200x675.jpg"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772625292_RJTePVeL9q-SHOWSHA-VAL-5jpg-rwGT5cnFc3-1200x720.jpg"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772625292_RJTePVeL9q-SHOWSHA-VAL-5jpg-rwGT5cnFc3-1200x720.jpg"}}},"intro":"‘Bigg Boss 19’ fame personalities lit up a star-studded Holi bash in Mumbai as TV celebs celebrated the festival of colours in style. Manisha Kumari was spotted enjoying the festivities among the crowd, while Ashnoor Kaur impressed with her vibrant appearance and camaraderie with fellow participants. Gaurav Khanna and other TV stars embraced the festive spirit with lively colours, music and fashion-forward looks, making the party a fashionable Holi affair.#Holi2026 #MumbaiHoliBash #TVCelebs","liveblog_api_url":{"status":0,"title":"","blog_url":""},"has_video":false,"meta_description":"‘Bigg Boss 19’ fame personalities lit up a star-studded Holi bash in Mumbai as TV celebs celebrated the festival of colours in style. Manisha Kumari was spotted enjoying the festivities among the crowd, while Ashnoor Kaur impressed with her vibrant appearance and camaraderie with fellow participants. Gaurav Khanna and other TV stars embraced the festive spirit with lively colours, music and fashion-forward looks, making the party a fashionable Holi affair.\n\n#Holi2026 #MumbaiHoliBash #TVCelebs","post_type":"video","story_id":9942356,"updated_at":"2026-03-04 17:24:43","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/videos/movies/bigg-boss-fame-manisha-kumari-ashnoor-kaur-gaurav-khanna-dazzle-at-