ll-black ensemble for the New York City premiere of the show. The 58-year-old actor opted for an oversized double-breasted black blazer featuring gold buttons, which she paired with a semi-sheer black skirt detailed with feather-like accents. Watch the video for a closer look.\n","post_type":"video","story_id":9942021,"updated_at":"2026-03-04 14:00:00","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/videos/movies/nicole-kidman-stuns-in-a-chic-all-black-fit-at-scarpetta-new-york-premiere-n18g-9942021.html","weburl_r":"/videos/movies/nicole-kidman-stuns-in-a-chic-all-black-fit-at-scarpetta-new-york-premiere-n18g-9942021.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Movies","Videos"],"categories":[{"id":15,"name":"Movies","slug":"movies","parent":0,"permalink":0},{"id":1779270,"name":"Videos","slug":"videos","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-03-04 14:00:00","display_headline":"Sachin, Sara, Anjali, Raj Thackeray, Yuvraj Singh, Irfan Pathan At Arjun Tendulkar's Sangeet","headline":"Sachin, Sara, Anjali, Raj Thackeray, Yuvraj Singh, Irfan Pathan At Arjun Tendulkar's Sangeet","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772613005_oHsGNycDUx-thumbnail1772610625421jpg-PY5pMSLX7r-1200x720.jpg","caption":"","alt":""},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/jpeg","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772613005_oHsGNycDUx-thumbnail1772610625421jpg-PY5pMSLX7r.jpg","caption":"News18","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772613005_oHsGNycDUx-thumbnail1772610625421jpg-PY5pMSLX7r-1200x675.jpg"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772613005_oHsGNycDUx-thumbnail1772610625421jpg-PY5pMSLX7r-1200x720.jpg"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772613005_oHsGNycDUx-thumbnail1772610625421jpg-PY5pMSLX7r-1200x720.jpg"}}},"intro":"Arjun Tendulkar’s sangeet was nothing short of a full-blown starry celebration! The evening saw the Tendulkar family coming together in style, with Sachin Tendulkar arriving alongside wife Anjali and daughter Sara, making it a complete family moment. The guest list, though, truly stole the spotlight. Yuvraj Singh made a stylish appearance with wife Hazel Keech, while Harbhajan Singh also joined the celebrations. Raj Thackeray was spotted arriving as well. Watch the video to know more.","liveblog_api_url":{"status":0,"title":"","blog_url":""},"has_video":false,"meta_description":"Arjun Tendulkar’s sangeet was nothing short of a full-blown starry celebration! The evening saw the Tendulkar family coming together in style, with Sachin Tendulkar arriving alongside wife Anjali and daughter Sara, making it a complete family moment. The guest list, though, truly stole the spotlight. Yuvraj Singh made a stylish appearance with wife Hazel Keech, while Harbhajan Singh also joined the celebrations. Raj Thackeray was spotted arriving as well. Watch the video to know more.\n","post_type":"video","story_id":9942017,"updated_at":"2026-03-04 14:00:00","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/videos/movies/arjun-tendulkars-sangeet-sachin-sara-anjali-raj-thackeray-yuvraj-singh-irfan-pathan-attend-9942017.html","weburl_r":"/videos/movies/arjun-tendulkars-sangeet-sachin-sara-anjali-raj-thackeray-yuvraj-singh-irfan-pathan-attend-9942017.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Movies","Videos"],"categories":[{"id":15,"name":"Movies","slug":"movies","parent":0,"permalink":0},{"id":1779270,"name":"Videos","slug":"videos","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-03-04 12:20:41","display_headline":"Holi 2026: Ranbir Kapoor, Vicky Kaushal, Katrina Kaif, Varun Dhawan \u0026 MORE Paint B-Town Bright","headline":"Holi 2026: Ranbir Kapoor, Vicky Kaushal, Katrina Kaif, Varun Dhawan \u0026 MORE Paint B-Town Bright","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772607054_WXPSwXwg24-THUMBS-png-hdNqrblU3b-1200x720.png","caption":"","alt":""},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/png","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772607054_WXPSwXwg24-THUMBS-png-hdNqrblU3b.png","caption":"News18","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772607054_WXPSwXwg24-THUMBS-png-hdNqrblU3b-1200x675.png"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772607054_WXPSwXwg24-THUMBS-png-hdNqrblU3b-1200x720.png"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772607054_WXPSwXwg24-THUMBS-png-hdNqrblU3b-1200x720.png"}}},"intro":"Holi 2026 is here, and our dear B-Towners are soaking in the true spirit of the festival of colour. From RK’s adorable daddy-daughter moment with Raha to Katrina’s cosy family celebration with Vicky Kaushal, along with Kriti Sanon keeping it warm with sweet family snaps and Varun Dhawan’s love-soaked moments, it was truly a treat for Bollywood hearts. Here’s a look at all the unmissable Holi highlights from Bollywood.","liveblog_api_url":{"status":0,"title":"","blog_url":""},"has_video":false,"meta_description":"Holi 2026 is here, and our dear B-Towners are soaking in the true spirit of the festival of colour. From RK’s adorable daddy-daughter moment with Raha to Katrina’s cosy family celebration with Vicky Kaushal, along with Kriti Sanon keeping it warm with sweet family snaps and Varun Dhawan’s love-soaked moments, it was truly a treat for Bollywood hearts. Here’s a look at all the unmissable Holi highlights from Bollywood.","post_type":"video","story_id":9941812,"updated_at":"2026-03-04 12:20:41","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/videos/movies/holi-2026-ranbir-kapoor-vicky-kaushal-katrina-kaif-varun-dhawan-more-paint-b-town-bright-9941812.html","weburl_r":"/videos/movies/holi-2026-ranbir-kapoor-vicky-kaushal-katrina-kaif-varun-dhawan-more-paint-b-town-bright-9941812.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Movies","Videos"],"categories":[{"id":15,"name":"Movies","slug":"movies","parent":0,"permalink":0},{"id":1779270,"name":"Videos","slug":"videos","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-03-03 18:20:17","display_headline":"Cillian Murphy Premieres 'Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man' In Birmingham | N18G","headline":"Cillian Murphy Premieres 'Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man' In Birmingham | N18G","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772542233_IAhX0Rbp1L-THUMBS-png-K0hhNZIaTV-1200x720.png","caption":"","alt":""},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/png","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772542233_IAhX0Rbp1L-THUMBS-png-K0hhNZIaTV.png","caption":"News18","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772542233_IAhX0Rbp1L-THUMBS-png-K0hhNZIaTV-1200x675.png"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772542233_IAhX0Rbp1L-THUMBS-png-K0hhNZIaTV-1200x720.png"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772542233_IAhX0Rbp1L-THUMBS-png-K0hhNZIaTV-1200x720.png"}}},"intro":"The Shelby legacy returns as Cillian Murphy reprises his iconic role in 'Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man'. Premiering in Birmingham, the film reunites Murphy with creator Steven Knight and director Tom Harper, bringing the gritty world of the hit series 'Peaky Blinders' to the big screen. Featuring powerhouse additions like Barry Keoghan, Rebecca Ferguson and Tim Roth, the cast promises a cinematic punch packed into one explosive film. From emotional reunions to bold new characters, this next chapter of Tommy Shelby’s saga is set to thrill both longtime fans and newcomers alike. Watch this video for more.","liveblog_api_url":{"status":0,"title":"","blog_url":""},"has_video":false,"meta_description":"The Shelby legacy returns as Cillian Murphy reprises his iconic role in 'Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man'. Premiering in Birmingham, the film reunites Murphy with creator Steven Knight and director Tom Harper, bringing the gritty world of the hit series 'Peaky Blinders' to the big screen. Featuring powerhouse additions like Barry Keoghan, Rebecca Ferguson and Tim Roth, the cast promises a cinematic punch packed into one explosive film. From emotional reunions to bold new characters, this next chapter of Tommy Shelby’s saga is set to thrill both longtime fans and newcomers alike. Watch this video for more.","post_type":"video","story_id":9941029,"updated_at":"2026-03-03 18:20:17","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/videos/movies/cillian-murphy-premieres-peaky-blinders-the-immortal-man-in-birmingham-n18g-9941029.html","weburl_r":"/videos/movies/cillian-murphy-premieres-peaky-blinders-the-immortal-man-in-birmingham-n18g-9941029.html","app_first":0},{"section":["Movies","Videos"],"categories":[{"id":15,"name":"Movies","slug":"movies","parent":0,"permalink":0},{"id":1779270,"name":"Videos","slug":"videos","parent":0,"permalink":0}],"created_at":"2026-03-03 18:01:24","display_headline":"Bollywood Celebs Richa Chadha, Ali Fazal, Urmila Matondkar Join Shabana Azmi \u0026 Javed Akhtar’s Holi B","headline":"Bollywood Celebs Richa Chadha, Ali Fazal, Urmila Matondkar Join Shabana Azmi \u0026 Javed Akhtar’s Holi B","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772541089_aZv2LbbDVg-SHOWSHA-VAL-4jpg-9lZtYvfQKt-1200x720.jpg","caption":"","alt":""},"images_all_sizes":{"mime_type":"image/jpeg","url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772541089_aZv2LbbDVg-SHOWSHA-VAL-4jpg-9lZtYvfQKt.jpg","caption":"News18","sizes":{"16x9":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772541089_aZv2LbbDVg-SHOWSHA-VAL-4jpg-9lZtYvfQKt-1200x675.jpg"},"4x3":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772541089_aZv2LbbDVg-SHOWSHA-VAL-4jpg-9lZtYvfQKt-1200x720.jpg"},"3x2":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/03/1772541089_aZv2LbbDVg-SHOWSHA-VAL-4jpg-9lZtYvfQKt-1200x720.jpg"}}},"intro":"Shabana Azmi and Javed Akhtar hosted a vibrant Holi celebration at their Mumbai home, drawing Bollywood stars including Richa Chadha, Ali Fazal and Urmila Matondkar to revel in colours, music and dance. The festive gathering hi