nlive/uploads/2026/01/Union-Budget-8-2026-01-bac4ca0dae4ab27a27d50878014fc711-3x2.jpeg","caption":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman will present the annual budget on February 1, 2026.","alt":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman will present the annual economic survey on Jan 29, 2026."},"liveblog_switcher":0},{"story_id":9853202,"display_headline":"Budget 2026 To Be Tabled On February 1: Know The Basics, Process And Key FAQs | Explained","headline":"Budget 2026 To Be Tabled On February 1: Know The Basics, Process And Key FAQs | Explained","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/business/economy/budget-2026-to-be-tabled-on-february-1-know-the-basics-process-and-key-faqs-explained-ws-l-9853202.html","weburl_r":"/business/economy/budget-2026-to-be-tabled-on-february-1-know-the-basics-process-and-key-faqs-explained-ws-l-9853202.html","intro":"This will be Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman's ninth consecutive Union Budget, which will also be India's 88th Budget since Independence. Here's all you need to know:","images":{"url":"https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/01/Union-Budget-8-2026-01-bac4ca0dae4ab27a27d50878014fc711-3x2.jpeg","caption":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman will present the annual budget on February 1, 2026.","alt":"FM Nirmala Sitharaman will present the annual economic survey on Jan 29, 2026."},"liveblog_switcher":0},{"story_id":9851208,"display_headline":"Budget 2026: Life Insurers Seek Tax Parity, Affordability Push To Boost Retirement Coverage","headline":"Budget 2026: Life Insurers Seek Tax Parity, Affordability Push To Boost Retirement Coverage","weburl":"https://www.news18.com/business/budget-2026-life-insurers-seek-tax-parity-affordability-push-to-boost-retirement-coverage-ws-l-9851208.html","weburl_r":"/business/budget-2026-life-insurers-seek-tax-parity-affordability-push-to-boost-retirement-coverage-ws-l-9851208.html","intro":"Tarun Chugh of Bajaj Life Insurance urges the Union Budget to boost life insurance via tax parity, affordability, and rural access.","images":{"url":"h